SUMMARY:Global Game Jam 2026
DESCRIPTION:Global Game Jam is the world’s largest game creation event … and directly serves 40\,000 game creators every year in 100+ countries. More than just a 48-hour game jam\, GGJ has been a starting point for hundreds of thousands of game developers around the world who have built successful\, sustainable careers in game development\, launched studios and created award-winning games. Throughout the year\, we work to support our community of jammers through community engagement\, partner jams and more. \nJoin BIG as we participate in GGJ 2026!
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/global-game-jam-2026/
LOCATION:MD
END:VEVENT
